## Practical Implementation Tips

### **1. Prompt Variables/Placeholders**

Your prompts use placeholders like `{TITLE}`, `{COUNT}`, etc. The agent fills these:

```markdown
<!-- In bulk-create.md -->
Create {COUNT} items of type {CONTENT_TYPE}

<!-- Agent processes this as: -->
Count = 5
Content_Type = "article"
Then executes create-article.md 5 times
```

### **2. Context Passing Between Prompts**

```markdown
<!-- Step 1: create-taxonomy-term.md creates "Technology" category -->
Result: taxonomy_term_id = 42

<!-- Step 2: create-article.md receives this context -->
"In the category field, select term ID 42"
```

### **3. Conditional Prompt Loading**

```markdown
<!-- Agent logic: -->
IF request contains "with image" THEN
  use create-with-media.md
ELSE
  use create-article.md
END IF
```

